# xtraCHEF Recipes
#
# How to find your Tenant ID and Location ID:
#   1. Log into https://app.sa.toasttab.com
#   2. Open DevTools (F12) → Network tab
#   3. Navigate to Recipes (app.sa.toasttab.com/Recipe/Recipe/NewRecipe)
#   4. Look for a request to ecs-api-prod.sa.toasttab.com containing "recipe-summary"
#      The URL looks like: .../recipes-v2/tenants/{TENANT_ID}/location/{LOCATION_ID}/recipe-summary
#   5. Copy the numeric TENANT_ID and LOCATION_ID from that URL
#
# How to get your session cookie:
#   1. In the same DevTools Network tab, click the recipe-summary request
#   2. Under "Request Headers", find the "Cookie:" header
#   3. Copy the entire cookie string value
#   4. Paste it here OR paste it in the Settings page UI (Settings → xtraCHEF → Session cookie)
#   Note: The cookie expires when your browser session ends. You'll need to
#   re-copy it periodically. The Settings page UI is easier for updates.
#
XTRACHEF_TENANT_ID=39494
XTRACHEF_LOCATION_ID=12802
XTRACHEF_COOKIE=

# Cron secret (GitHub Actions -> API routes, also used to sign session tokens)
CRON_SECRET=your-cron-secret

# Dashboard password (simple auth gate for the web UI)
DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=your-dashboard-password
